\item Run \code{diagnose_mfrm(fit, residual_pca = "none")} for baseline diagnostics.
\item Inspect \code{summary(diag)} and targeted tables/plots.
\item If needed, rerun with residual PCA (\code{"overall"} or \code{"both"}).
